name: TheGhosty.GitHub.io
tagline: This is George Trickett (TheGhosty)'s GitHub Page!
body:
Hello there! You've found my GitHub page! If you were looking for it congratulations!

If you are here to contact me to discuss my work, I don't bite (often... ) so please contact me via Twitter @GTrick_ I'm very friendly and usually willing to help with any issues/questions you may have.


Not sure how useful this page will be... But I guess we'll find out!

~TheGhosty
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
